title: Jenkins and Jonez - John Is A Dad! And The Rest Of The World Is Falling Apart
itunes:title: Jenkins and Jonez - John Is A Dad! And The Rest Of The World Is Falling Apart
description:
John returns to the pod as a new dad and discusses how fatherhood has already changed him with Tyler and Mike (3:00), before discussing the Robert Sarver article (15:30), Aaron Rodgers revealing himself as an anti-vaxxer (26:30), Luka Doncic’s new haircut (42:00), and more.
